<br />\n<strong>4. 下次香港人未必有得抽, 因為美國已取消香港的特殊地位, 中國籍人士係冇得抽架</strong>"},{"pid":"bfaab795deb2d52357f36204d13eb629516be189","tid":2177802,"uid":208296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:51:46.000Z","msg":"抽中左都可以reject你"},{"pid":"768586c0a625db9e35b58e4d86a7ac1dd5efa70a","tid":2177802,"uid":325139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T21:22:40.000Z","msg":"DV 2022 已經僦香港份，但澳門仲有：<br />\n<br />\nNatives of the following Asia Region countries are <strong>not eligible</strong> for this year&rsquo;s Diversity Visa program:<br />\r\nBangladesh, <strong>China including Hong Kong</strong>), India, Pakistan, South Korea, Philippines, and Vietnam. <br />\n<br />\n** Macau S.A.R. (Europe region, chargeable to Portugal) and Taiwan (Asia region) do qualify and are listed. For <br />\r\nthe purposes of the diversity program only, persons born in Macau S.A.R. derive eligibility from Portugal.<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://travel.state.gov/content/dam/visas/Diversity-Visa/DV-Instructions-Translations/DV-2022-Instructions-Translations/DV-2022-Instructions-and-FAQs_English.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.state.gov%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fvisas%2FDiversity-Visa%2FDV-Instructions-Translations%2FDV-2022-Instructions-Translations%2FDV-2022-Instructions-and-FAQs_English.pdf&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=42cc2a57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://travel.state.gov/content/dam/visas/Diversity-Visa/DV-Instructions-Translations/DV-2022-Instructions-Translations/DV-2022-Instructions-and-FAQs_English.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nBTW, 有無成功人仕分享成功抽到的經驗？<br />\n<br />\n利申： 澳門人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}